254
00:19:44.577 --> 00:19:47.580
Jeg mener, du har Dr. King, krigen.

255
00:19:49.499 --> 00:19:53.461
Jeg tror ikke, at lyriske metaforer
holder mere.


256
00:19:53.503 --> 00:19:54.629
Hvad?
Imponeret over de svære ord?


257
00:19:55.463 --> 00:19:57.507
Ja.

258
00:19:58.633 --> 00:20:01.594
